<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 14:04:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>创纪录的热浪袭击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/record-breaking-heat-wave-hits-israel/0000018f-1548-dc39-a9cf-b5ce79ab0000</link><description>以色列气象局执行主任阿米尔·吉瓦蒂博士说，像这样的热浪是全球变暖趋势的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:25:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/record-breaking-heat-wave-hits-israel/0000018f-1548-dc39-a9cf-b5ce79ab0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登和其他 17 名世界领导人呼吁立即释放加沙哈马斯扣押的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-17-other-world-leaders-call-for-immediate-release-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza/0000018f-155c-d361-a3ef-57fd397b0001</link><description>一名美国高级官员否认了有关以色列是达成人质释放协议的主要障碍的指控，并将责任完全归咎于哈马斯。信中呼吁哈马斯释放人质，以实现加沙立即长期停火</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:17:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-17-other-world-leaders-call-for-immediate-release-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza/0000018f-155c-d361-a3ef-57fd397b0001</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列艺术家对法国大师的改造令巴黎印象深刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-artist-whose-twist-on-french-masters-is-impressing-paris/0000018f-10ca-d97f-abcf-fccb10fa0000</link><description>在奥赛博物馆的展览中，纳塔娜埃尔·赫柏林的作品被放置在法国革命后印象派画家的画作旁边。她告诉国土报她如何继承这一遗产</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-artist-whose-twist-on-french-masters-is-impressing-paris/0000018f-10ca-d97f-abcf-fccb10fa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院下令无条件释放在耶路撒冷人质游行中被捕的抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-unconditional-release-of-protesters-arrested-at-jerusalem-hostage-march/0000018f-1502-d2e1-a7df-15a666110000</link><description>在哈马斯发布一段显示以色列裔美国人赫什·戈德堡-波林在加沙被囚禁的视频后不久，数百人在耶路撒冷游行寻求释放人质，两名抗议者被捕</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:05:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-unconditional-release-of-protesters-arrested-at-jerusalem-hostage-march/0000018f-1502-d2e1-a7df-15a666110000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列战争中，美国的熊抱注定会变得更紧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/americas-bear-hug-is-fated-to-grow-tighter-amid-israels-wars/0000018f-14e7-d361-a3ef-56f7c8a10000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列在财政和军事上比以往任何时候都更加依赖美国。内塔尼亚胡正在让以色列在未来几年变得更加依赖</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 11:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/americas-bear-hug-is-fated-to-grow-tighter-amid-israels-wars/0000018f-14e7-d361-a3ef-56f7c8a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人真的能再次选举内塔尼亚胡吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/could-israelis-seriously-elect-netanyahu-again/0000018f-140f-d2e1-a7df-15af86a10000</link><description>以色列最新的民意调查给​​了本雅明·内塔尼亚胡和他狂热的联盟伙伴自10月7日以来的最高分数。但这只是在以色列总理的政治生涯最终结束之前，以色列对伊朗的谨慎反应所推动的短暂现象吗？</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 09:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/could-israelis-seriously-elect-netanyahu-again/0000018f-140f-d2e1-a7df-15af86a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁在特拉维夫讨论续签加沙谈判，数十人集会争取人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article-live/hundreds-of-israelis-march-after-hamas-releases-hostage-video/0000018f-12f8-df8a-afcf-bffbe6cb0000</link><description