武装分子已被消灭” ■ 佩洛西呼吁内塔尼亚胡辞职 ■ 战争进入 201 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:46:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-201-idf-says-it-mobilized-two-reserve-brigades-to-south-gaza/0000018f-10a5-d361-a3ef-52f5c1340001</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯播放视频显示以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-showing-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin-in-gaza/0000018f-10d7-d361-a3ef-52f7a0400000</link><description>戈德堡-波林在 10 月 7 日的诺瓦节上哈马斯袭击中受重伤，并在视频中出现手臂被截肢的情况。数百名抗议者在耶路撒冷和特拉维夫游行，他们称之为视频发布引发的“愤怒示威”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:43:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-showing-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin-in-gaza/0000018f-10d7-d361-a3ef-52f7a0400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级官员承认阻止近东救济工程处国际资助的行动失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-officials-acknowledge-failure-of-campaign-to-halt-unrwa-international-funding/0000018f-104e-d97f-abcf-fccf9f300000</link><description>德国加入了宣布将继续向联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构提供资金的国家行列。以色列担心英国和美国也会改变冻结资金的决定</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:22:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-officials-acknowledge-failure-of-campaign-to-halt-unrwa-international-funding/0000018f-104e-d97f-abcf-fccf9f300000</guid></item><item><title>北京电影节在抵制浪潮中取消放映以色列电影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/beijing-film-festival-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-amid-wave-of-boycotts/0000018f-1094-df8a-afcf-bf9fbc420000</link><description>以色列故事片《城市》原定本月在中国电影节上放映，但在与以色列发行商密切接触数周后，电影节突然取消了制作团队的航班和电影的放映，且没有任何解释</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/beijing-film-festival-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-amid-wave-of-boycotts/0000018f-1094-df8a-afcf-bf9fbc420000</guid></item><item><title>拜登签署以色列国防援助法案，称交付即将进行；要求以色列确保对加沙的援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/biden-signs-israel-defense-bill-says-delivery-imminent-demands-israel-ensures-gaza-aid/0000018f-10b4-d361-a3ef-52f5f2cd0000</link><description>该法案包括向以色列提供260亿美元、向加沙提供10亿美元的人道主义援助，以及向乌克兰和台湾提供的援助。参议院的反对者和众议院一样，包括左翼参议员，他们因以色列轰炸造成数千名加沙人丧生而反对援助。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/biden-signs-israel-defense-bill-says-delivery-imminent-demands-israel-ensures-gaza-aid/0000018f-10b4-d361-a3ef-52f5f2cd0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长表示将投票支持特朗普：拜登对以色列关系“造成真正损害”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-says-he-would-vote-for-trump-biden-strategy-hurts-israel/0000018f-104e-d70d-a58f-d9ffb9d20000</link><description>就在美国参议院批准对以色列具有里程碑意义的 140 亿美元军事援助计划数小时后，侨民部长阿米猜·奇克利 (Amichai Chikli) 表示，如果可以的话，他将投票给前总统特朗普，因为拜登政府“不允许以色列按照自己的意愿运作”。拉法&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-says-he-would-vote-for-trump-biden-strategy-hurts-israel/0000018f-104e-d70d-a58f-d9ffb9d20000</guid></item><item><title>解释：想要重建圣殿的以色列极端分子以及支持他们的政府部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-extremists-who-want-to-rebuild-the-temple-and-the-ministers-who-back-them/0000018f-0f34-d97f-abcf-efbd07d50000</link><description>他们梦想重建圣殿，重新实行动物祭祀，并让犹太宗教垄断世界上最具争议、易燃易爆的地点之一——圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺。它曾经是一个边缘运动，但现在得到了伊塔马尔·本格维尔和内塔尼亚胡政府中其他极右极端分子的支持。这就是圣殿运动的故事</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:28:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-extremists-who-want-to-rebuild-the-temple-and-the-ministers-who-back-them/0000018f-0f34-d97f-abcf-efbd07d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官辞职会引发雪崩吗？不是最重要的地方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/will-resignations-by-israeli-army-officers-start-an-avalanche-not-where-it-matters-most/0000018f-0fed-dc39-a9cf-bfefb3f00000</link><description>以色列军事情报局长的离职可能为短期内其他公开退出铺平了道路。自10月7日以来，内塔尼亚胡除了试图为自己开脱之外什么也没做，他很可能会以此作为自己无罪的证据</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/will-resignations-by-israeli-army-officers-start-an-avalanche-not-where-it-matters-most/0000018f-0fed-dc39-a9cf-bfefb3f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与温和阿拉伯国家之间的联盟能维持多久？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-long-can-the-alliance-between-israel-and-moderate-arab-states-survive/0000018f-0f7f-d361-a3ef-4fff918f0000</link><description>以色列的地区伙伴——约旦、沙特阿拉伯和其他国家——帮助抵御了伊朗的袭击。但这些联盟的韧性已经因加沙战争而受到压力，更不用说更全面的一体化了，这要求以色列致力于建立一个独立的巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 12:41:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-long-can-the-alliance-between-israel-and-moderate-arab-states-survive/0000018f-0f7f-d361-a3ef-4fff918f0000</guid></item><item><title>德国将恢复与巴勒斯坦近东救济工程处的合作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/germany-plans-to-resume-unrwa-cooperation-after-independent-report/0000018f-0fd2-d97f-abcf-efdb527d0000</link><description>这一决定是在联合国要求的一项调查发现没有证据支持以色列关于十几名近东救济工程处员工参与了 10 月 7 日对以色列的袭击的指控之后作出的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 11:42:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/germany-plans-to-resume-unrwa-cooperation-after-independent-report/0000018f-0fd2-d97f-abcf-efdb527d0000</guid></item><item><title>斯莫特里奇赞扬以色列军事情报负责人辞职，称以色列国防军负责人无法任命继任者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-lauds-military-intel-head-resignation-says-idf-chief-cannot-appoint-successor/0000018f-0f95-df8a-afcf-af9f2e610000</link><description>极右翼财政部长表示，军事情报局局长阿哈龙·哈利瓦声称对10月7日的失败负责，这是改变以色列军队指挥结构的一个机会，但没有提及政府的责任</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 11:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-lauds-military-intel-head-resignation-says-idf-chief-cannot-appoint-successor/0000018f-0f95-df8a-afcf-af9f2e610000</guid></item></channel></rss>